      underside: "No gills, pores or teeth; the fertile surface covers the gelatinous lobes. Basidia ellipsoid to roughly spherical, 15–21 μm wide, longitudinally septate (two to four septa). Spores broadly ellipsoid to oblong, on average 10–16 by 6–9.5 μm.",
